“**Chrono-Echo Weave: A Sensory Time Capsule** - A neuro-reactive textile garment that records and recreates fragmented memories through dynamically shifting sonic and haptic landscapes generated by analyzing real-time movement data. Imagine: a subtle tremor as you walk down a familiar street triggers a ripple of synthesized sounds – the laughter of a child, the scent of rain, a snippet of a song – all woven into a tactile experience, designed to evoke a specific memory. The garment learns *your* unique movement signature, becoming increasingly accurate over time. It’s like carrying a piece of your past with you, constantly reshaping itself based on your movement and the echoes of your recollections. We could even add scent diffusion – a tiny, bio-engineered spore dispersal system releasing carefully curated aromas linked to each memory!”